  "extra_note_en": "Vowel harmony determines -ecek or -acak. Most future meanings use this one structure (unlike English which splits into 'will' and 'be going to'). Time expressions: yarın (tomorrow), gelecek hafta (next week), yakında (soon), bir saat sonra (in an hour), 2026'da (in 2026), etc. The future tense is very regular – just learn vowel harmony and negation with -me/-ma."
